# PROJECT: Habit Pet - Android MVP (Version 1)

You are a senior Android engineer, Kotlin architect, UI/UX designer, game systems designer, and product manager.

Your task is to design and implement a complete Android application from scratch called **Habit Pet**.

The project must be production-quality, cleanly architected, and fully runnable in Android Studio.

Build a complete working application.

Use production-quality architecture and implementations.

Placeholder visual assets are acceptable when required.

---

# PRODUCT VISION

Habit Pet is not a habit tracker.

Habit Pet is a virtual companion game where users maintain real-life habits in order to help a virtual pet grow and evolve.

The emotional focus is the pet.

The habit tracking system exists only to support the pet progression system.

The app must feel:

* Warm
* Rewarding
* Motivating
* Cute
* Addictive in a positive way
* Never punishing

Users should feel emotionally attached to their pet.

