# HABIT SYSTEM

Users can create habits.

Fields:

* id
* name
* icon
* type
* minimumDurationMinutes

Habit types:

1. CHECKBOX
2. TIMER

---

# CHECKBOX HABITS

Examples:

* Skincare
* Vitamins
* Make Bed

User presses:

COMPLETE

Done.

---

# TIMER HABITS

Examples:

* Workout
* Reading
* Study

Flow:

Press Start

Timer begins

Press Finish

If elapsed time >= minimum duration:

Complete habit

Award XP

Otherwise:

Display remaining time needed

---

# DAILY COMPLETION

Only one completion per habit per day.

Prevent duplicates.

---

# STREAK SYSTEM

Each habit tracks:

Current streak

Best streak

Global streak system also exists.

Global streak means:

All habits scheduled today completed.

Global streak is displayed on Home Screen.

---

# IMPORTANT RULE

Missing a day:

Reset streak

DO NOT:

* Remove XP
* Remove pet levels
* Remove unlocked items
* Remove rewards

Progress should never feel destroyed.

