NOT current streak.

---

# PET LIFE SYSTEM

Pet must appear alive.

This is extremely important.

The pet should have animations.

Use sprite animations, Lottie, frame animations, or Compose animation systems.

Do not leave the pet static.

---

# EGG BEHAVIOR

Level 0

Egg idle.

Very subtle floating animation.

---

After user earns some XP:

Egg occasionally wiggles.

Rare.

---

Near hatching threshold:

Egg wiggles frequently.

Small cracks appear.

---

At hatch evolution:

Play hatching animation.

Egg breaks.

Dragon emerges.

Confetti effect.

Reward screen.

---

# HATCHLING BEHAVIOR

Animations:

* Blink
* Breathing
* Tail wag
* Happy bounce

Random idle animations every few seconds.

---

# YOUNG DRAGON

